":menuselection:`CRM` qui sont dans l'étape *Gagnée* et ont un revenu attendu "
"supérieur à 1 000 $, saisir ce qui suit :"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/search.rst:140
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Match all` :icon:`fa-caret-down` :guilabel:`of the following "
"rules:`"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Correspond à toutes` :icon:`fa-caret-down` :guilabel:`les règles "
"suivantes :`"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/search.rst:142
msgid ":guilabel:`Stage` :guilabel:`is in` :guilabel:`Won`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Étape` :guilabel:`est dans` :guilabel:`Gagnée`"

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/search.rst:143
msgid ":guilabel:`Expected Revenue` :guilabel:`>` `1,000`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Revenu attendu` :guilabel:`>` `1 000`"

